divs: Sighting DetailsI was walking through the woods, taking pictures of the wildlife, when I heard a strange humming sound. I looked up to see a large grayish shiny flying hotdog type craft. I pulled out my camera to take a picture of it, but the battery was suddenly drained. I stood and stared at the space craft for about five minutes. It then shot off westward to the mountains.
trends: There have been no other sightings in McCall
